sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Dashboard
    participant Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Dashboard: Views Job Tracker
    Dashboard->>Backend: GET /api/job-applications
    Backend->>DB: Fetch user applications
    DB-->>Backend: List<JobApplication>
    Backend-->>Dashboard: Return JSON array
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Render Kanban/Table + Analytics

    User->>Dashboard: Click "Create from Cover Letter"
    Dashboard->>Backend: POST /api/job-applications (status: SAVED)
    Backend->>DB: Check CoverLetter ID
    Backend->>DB: Create JobApplication Entity
    DB-->>Backend: Created Entity
    Backend-->>Dashboard: Return New Application
    Dashboard->>User: Display Success Toast

    User->>Dashboard: Update Status to "INTERVIEWING"
    Dashboard->>Backend: PUT /api/job-applications/{id}/status
    Backend->>DB: Update Status
    Backend-->>Dashboard: 200 OK
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Refresh Analytics KPIs
